1. Introduction
--------------
MR.COFFEE is a modern, responsive website designed for a futuristic coffee shop that seamlessly blends innovation with tradition. This documentation provides comprehensive information about the website's architecture, features, and implementation details.

2. Project Overview
------------------
The website serves as a digital platform for MR.COFFEE, featuring:
• Interactive menu system
• Online ordering capabilities
• Rewards program
• Company information
• Mobile-first responsive design

3. Project Structure
-------------------
The project follows a clear and organized file structure:

mrcoffe/
├── css/           - Contains all stylesheet files
├── js/           - Contains JavaScript functionality
├── images/       - Stores all image assets
├── index.html    - Main homepage
├── menu.html     - Menu display page
├── order.html    - Order processing page
├── rewards.html  - Rewards program page
└── about.html    - Company information page

4. Features
-----------
4.1 Home Page (index.html)
• Banner section with company slogan
• Featured products showcase
• Rewards program preview
• CEO & founder introduction

4.2 Menu Page (menu.html)
• Interactive menu filtering
• Product categorization
• Streamlined ordering process
• Dynamic price display

4.3 Order Page (order.html)
• Intuitive order form
• Real-time validation
• Customizable options
• Dynamic pricing calculation

4.4 Rewards Page (rewards.html)
• Mobile app integration
• Current rewards display
• Download options for iOS and Android
• Member benefits information

4.5 About Us Page (about.html)
• Company history
• Mission and vision statements
• Interactive timeline
• Team information

